title: #93: The Night Stalker and Chem Trails with Eddie Bravo and Theo Von
description: Thank you for tuning in for another fun episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. Here is the episode everyone as been asking for, the Eddie Bravo  and Theo Von show that "Starts off by talking Night Stalker but then we get into Chem trails and then we circle back again to the Night Stalker" episode.  Thank you for all of your support!
